$lang['Similarly, after reaching 9 in Hexadecimal (represented by “F”), we start counting again at 10 (“10”). This pattern continues until we reach 15 (“1F”), at which point we reset back to 0 and begin counting again at 16 (“20”). This might sound confusing at first, but with a little practice, it will become second nature!'] = 'O cogo kelen na, an sera 9 ma Hɛksadesimali la (a jiralen bɛ ni “F” ye), an bɛ jate daminɛ kokura 10 (“10”) la. O cogoya in bɛ taa ɲɛ fo an ka se 15 (“1F”) ma, o waati la an bɛ segin ka segin 0 kan, ka jate daminɛ kokura 16 (“20”) la. O bɛ se ka kɛ ko i bɛ mɔgɔ hakili ɲagami a daminɛ na, nka ni i ye i yɛrɛ dege dɔɔnin, a bɛna kɛ fɛn filanan ye!';
